	function getMainBanner() {
		$.ajax({
			url: mainurl + '/call',
			dataType: 'json',
			type: 'POST',
			data: {
				cmd: 'MAIN_BANNER_VIEW',
				kind: 'MainPc'
			},
			success: setMainBanner,
			complete: getNotice
		})
	}

	function setMainBanner({body: {result}}) {
		let htm = '';

		if (!result) return;
		$.each(result, function (index, item) {
			if (index === 0) {
				if (item.imgId) {
					let img_link = item.img_link || '',
						img_desc = item.img_desc || '';
					htm += `<div class="imgbannerArea">
							<a href="javascript:goCuration(1,'${img_link}');"><img src="${mainimgurl + item.imgId}"  alt="${img_desc}"></a>
						</div>`;
				} else {
					htm += `<div class="videoArea">
						<div class="youtube_area">
						<img src="../resources/images/temp/dummy_youtube.png" class="img_dummy" alt="">
						<div id="ytplayer2">${item.img_title}</div>`;
					if (item.video_type === 'VR') {
						if (getDevice() === 'iOS') {
							let img_link = item.img_link;
							img_link = img_link.replace("https://youtu.be/", "");

							htm += `<div class="iosLayer" style="height : 100%;">
								<div>
									<p>  VR <br/>
									 Youtube APP <br/>
									  .</p>
									<a href="javascript:goYoutubeApp('${img_link}');">Youtube APP  </a>
								</div>
								<button type="button" onclick="closeIosLayer();"></button>
							</div>`;
						}
					}
					htm += `</div>`;
					setTimeout(video, 500);
				}
			}
		});
		$('#imgOrVideo').prepend(htm).show();
	};

	function video() {
		createVideo = true;
		initVideos();
	};

	function initVideos() {
		if (createVideo) {
			for (let i = 0; i < ytPlayerList.length; i++) {
				let player = ytPlayerList[i],
					pl = new YT.Player(player.DivId, {
						width: '100%',
						height: '100%',
						videoId: player.VideoId,
						playerVars: {
							rel: 0,
							playsinline: 1
						}
					});
				players[player.Id] = pl;
			}
		}
		/* 		setTimeout( function() {
					let layerheight = $('.youtube_area').height();
					$('.iosLayer').height(layerheight+"px");
				}, 1000); */
	}

	function getNotice() {
		$.ajax({
			url: mainurl + '/call',
			dataType: 'json',
			type: "POST",
			data: {
				cmd: 'MAIN_CURATION_VIEW',
				kind: 'MainPc'
			},
			success: setNotice,
			complete: promotion.getPromotion
		});
	}

	function setNotice({body: {result}}) {
		let htm = '';

		if (!result) return;
		const temp = result.filter(obj => obj.importantYn),
			rest = result.filter(obj => !obj.importantYn);
		result = temp.concat(rest);
		$.each(result, (index, item) => {
			let title = item.title,
				color = '';

			if (index < 4) {
				htm += '<li>';
				let linkurl = '';
				if (!item.cotId)
					htm += '<a href="javascript:" onclick=\'goCuration(1,"' + item.url + '")\' title="' + title + '  ">';
				else {
					switch(item.contentType){
						case '12':
							linkurl = "/detail/ms_detail.do?cotid=" + item.cotId;
							break;
						case '25':
							linkurl = "/detail/cs_detail.do?cotid=" + item.cotId;
							break;
						case '15':
							linkurl = "/detail/fes_detail.do?cotid=" + item.cotId;
							break;
						default:
							linkurl = !item.contentType || !item.contentType || item.contentType === '' ?
								"/detail/rem_detail.do?cotid=" + item.cotId + '&con_type=10000' :
								"/detail/rem_detail.do?cotid=" + item.cotId + '&con_type=' + item.contentType;
					}
					htm += '<a href="javascript:" onclick=\'goCuration(2,"' + linkurl + '");\' title="' + title + '  ">';
				}
				if (item.haederUse === 1) {
					color = "color:#" + item.haederColor;
					htm += `<em style="${color}" ${index === 0 && item.importantYn ? 'class="noti"' : ''}>${item.displayHeaderTitle}</em>`;
				}
				htm += title + '</a>';
				htm += '</li>';
			}
		});
		containerPC.find('.list_board').html(htm);
		temp.length === 0 && $container.find('.list_board li:eq(0)').addClass('non');
	}

	function goCuration(rkind, rurl) {
		goMainLogSave('9ea69225-9aa7-11e8-8165-020027310001');
		setTimeout(() => {
			if (rkind === 1) {
				if (rurl.indexOf(mainurl) > -1)
					location.href = rurl;
				else
					openWindow(rurl);
			} else
				location.href = mainurl + rurl;
		}, 200);
	}

	const promotion = {
		getPromotion: function(){
			$.ajax({
				url: mainurl + '/call',
				dataType: 'json',
				type: "POST",
				data: {
					cmd: 'NOTICE_PROMOTION_VIEW',
					kind: 'MainPc'
				},
				success: promotion.setPromotion,
				complete: getOdsBanner //  
			});
		},
		setPromotion: function({body: {result}}) {
			const con = $('#marketingBanner');
			let len,
				htm = ``,
				stackTypeN = 0,
				isNOpen,
				prevTypeW;

			if (!result) return;

			for(let i = 0; i < result.length; i++){
				const item = result[i],
					isTypeN = item.cgpType === '0',
					bgColor = item.bgColor ? ' style="background-color: ' + item.bgColor + ';"' : '';
				let isEvenStackTypeN;
				len = result.length;

				if(isTypeN && ++stackTypeN) {
					isEvenStackTypeN = stackTypeN % 2 === 0;
					if (!isEvenStackTypeN || prevTypeW){
						htm += `<div class="swiper-slide" ${bgColor}">
									<div class="type2">`;
						isNOpen = true;
					}
					htm += `			<div class="${!isEvenStackTypeN || prevTypeW ? 'left' : 'right'}" ${bgColor}>
											${makeContent()}
										</div>`;
				}
				if(isTypeN && isEvenStackTypeN || !isTypeN && isNOpen){
					htm += `
									</div>
								</div>`;
					isNOpen = false;
				}
				if(!isTypeN){
					if(isEvenStackTypeN && i !== len - 1){
						result.splice(i + 2, 0, item);
						continue;
					}
					htm += `<div class="swiper-slide" ${bgColor}">
								${makeContent()}
							</div>`;
				}
				prevTypeW = item.cgpType === '1';

				function makeContent(){
					return `<a href="javascript:" onclick="promotion.goMarketing('${item.cotId}', '${item.contentType}', '${item.linkUrl || ``}', '${quotReplace(item.title)}');" ${isTypeN ? ' class="cont"' : ''}>
								<span style="color:` + item.descColor + `">${item.description || ''}</span>
								<strong style="color:` + item.titleColor + `">${item.title || ''}</strong>
								<img src="${mainimgurl + item.imgPath}" alt="${item.imgAlt}">
							</a>`;
				}
			};
			con.show().find('.swiper-wrapper').html(htm);
			if(len > 2){
				con.find('.swiper-wrapper').after(`<div class="paging">
					<div class="btn_autoArea">
						<button class="btn_autoStop"></button>
					</div>
					<div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
				</div>`);
				promotion.marketingBannerSlide();
			}
		},
		marketingBannerSlide: function(){
			const swiper = new Swiper('.public_banner .type1 .swiper-container', {
				spaceBetween: 0,
				watchOverflow:true,
				slidesPerView: 1,
				loop: true,
				pagination: {
					el: '.public_banner .type1 .swiper-pagination',
					type: 'bullets',
					observer: true,
					observeParents: true,
					clickable: true,
					renderBullet: function (index, className) {
						return '<button type="button" class="' + className + '"><span class="blind">' + (index + 1) + '  </span></button>';
					}
				},
				autoplay: {
					delay: 5000,
				},
				on:{
					init: function () {
						swiperTabindex('.public_banner .type1', this.activeIndex);
					},
					slideChangeTransitionEnd: function () {
						swiperTabindex('.public_banner .type1', this.activeIndex);
					}
				}
			});
			$('.public_banner .type1').on('focusin', '.swiper-wrapper', function(){
				$(this).closest('.public_banner .type1').addClass('active');
				swiper.autoplay.stop();
				$('.public_banner .type1 .btn_autoArea button').text('');
			}).on('click', '.btn_autoArea button', function(){
				if($(this).closest('.public_banner .type1').hasClass('active')){
					$(this).closest('.public_banner .type1').removeClass('active');
					swiper.autoplay.start();
					$(this).text('');
				}else{
					$(this).closest('.public_banner .type1').addClass('active');
					swiper.autoplay.stop();
					$(this).text('');
				}
			}).on('click', '.swiper-pagination button', function(){
				if($('.public_banner .type1').addClass('active'))
					swiper.autoplay.stop();
			});
		},
		goMarketing: function(rcotid, rcontenttype, rlinkUrl, rtitle) {
			goMainLogSave('9a59d6f7-9aa7-11e8-8165-020027310001');
			if(!rlinkUrl) return;
			setTimeout(function () {
				goBannerLogSave('', rlinkUrl, rtitle);
			}, 200);
			setTimeout(() => {
				if (rlinkUrl)
					if (rlinkUrl.indexOf(mainurl) > -1)
						if (rlinkUrl.indexOf('tmap/main') > -1)
							if (isSizeM)
								if (appYn === 'Y')
									location.href = "opentab://" + rlinkUrl;
								else
									location.href = rlinkUrl;
							else
								location.href = rlinkUrl;
						else if (rlinkUrl.indexOf('windowopen') > -1)
							if (isSizeM)
								if (appYn === 'Y')
									location.href = "opentab://" + rlinkUrl;
								else
									window.open(rlinkUrl);
							else
								window.open(rlinkUrl, "", "width=540px,height=940px,status=yes,scrollbars=yes");
						else
							location.href = rlinkUrl;
					else
					if (appYn === 'Y')
						location.href = "opentab://" + rlinkUrl;
					else
						window.open(rlinkUrl);
				else
				if (rcontenttype == '12' || rcontenttype == '14' || rcontenttype == '28' || rcontenttype == '38' || rcontenttype == '39' || rcontenttype == '32' || rcontenttype == '2000')
					location.href = mainurl + '/detail/ms_detail.do?cotid=' + rcotid;
				else if (rcontenttype == '15')
					location.href = mainurl + '/detail/fes_detail.do?cotid=' + rcotid;
				else if (rcontenttype == '25')
					location.href = mainurl + '/detail/cs_detail.do?cotid=' + rcotid;
				else
				if (rcontenttype == undefined || rcontenttype == null || rcontenttype == '')
					location.href = mainurl + '/detail/rem_detail.do?cotid=' + rcotid + '&con_type=10000';
				else
					location.href = mainurl + '/detail/rem_detail.do?cotid=' + rcotid + '&con_type=' + rcontenttype;
			}, 200);
		}
	}

	function getOdsBanner() {
		$.ajax({
			url: mainurl + '/call',
			dataType: 'json',
			type: "POST",
			data: {
				cmd: 'ODS_BANNER_VIEW',
				kind: 'MainPc'
			},
			success: setOdsBanner,
			complete: () => getMainOtherTemp('Other') //  
		});
	}

	function setOdsBanner({body: {result}}) {
		let strHtml = '';

		if (!result) {
			$('#odsBanner').hide();
			return;
		}

		$.each(result, function (index, item) {
			if (index === 0)
				$('#odsBanner h2').html(item.title);

			if (item.lkOrder === 0)
				strHtml += '<li class="swiper-slide">';

			strHtml += '<div class="wrap">';
			strHtml += '	<a href="' + item.lkUrl + '"';
			if (item.lkType === 1) strHtml += ' target="_blank" title=""';
			strHtml += '>';
			strHtml += '		<span class="img"><img class="swiper-lazy" data-src="' + mainimgurl + item.imgId + '" alt="' + item.lkTitle + '"></span>';
			strHtml += '		<div class="text">';
			strHtml += '			<strong>' + item.lkTitle + '</strong>';
			strHtml += '			<span>go</span>';
			strHtml += '		</div>';
			strHtml += '	</a>';
			strHtml += '</div>';

			if (item.lkOrder === 1)
				strHtml += '</li>';
		});

		$('#odsBanner ul').html(strHtml);
	}

	function getMainOtherTemp(kind) {
		$.ajax({
			url: mainurl + '/call',
			dataType: 'json',
			type: "POST",
			data: {
				cmd: 'MAIN_OTHER_TEMP_VIEW',
				otdid: otdId
			},
			success: setMainOtherTemp,
			complete: homeEnd,
		});
	}

	function setMainOtherTemp(data) {
		const HOME = 'home',
			{body: {result}} = data,
			extract = (type) => result.filter(o => o.mainArea === type && o.templateId === '31')
				.reduce((acc, curr) => {
					const idx = curr.compOrder;
					acc[idx] = (acc[idx] || 0) + 1;
					return acc;
				}, []),
			cntObj = {
				D: extract('D'),
				E: extract('E')
			},
			htmObj = {D: '', E: ''};
		let other = '',
			temp = '';

		$.each(result, (idx, item) => {
			if (other === item.compId && item.templateId !== '31')
				return;
			const otdId = item.otdId,
				areakind = item.mainArea,
				odmid = item.odmId,
				compId = item.compId;
				other = item.compId;

			switch(item.templateId){
				case '1':
					temp = temp01(data, compId, HOME); break;
				case '2':
					temp = temp02(data, compId, HOME); break;
				case '3':
					temp = temp03(data, compId, HOME); break;
				case '4':
					temp = temp04(data, compId, HOME); break;
				case '5':
					temp = temp05(data, compId, HOME); break;
				case '6':
					temp = temp06(data, compId, HOME); break;
				case '7':
					temp = temp07(data, compId, HOME); break;
				case '8':
					temp = temp08(data, compId, HOME); break;
				case '9':
					temp = temp09(data, compId, odmid, HOME); break;
				case '13':
					temp = temp13(data, compId, HOME); break;
				case '14':
					temp = temp14(data, compId, HOME); break;
				case '23':
					temp = temp23(data, compId, HOME); break;
				case '31':
					htmObj[item.mainArea] += temp31(item, HOME, cntObj); break;
			}
			switch(areakind) {
				case 'A':
					$('#otherleft').append(temp); break;
				case 'B':
					$('#othermid').append(temp); break;
				case 'C':
					$('#otherright').append(temp); break;
			}
		});
		for (const key in htmObj)
			if (htmObj[key])
				$(`#horizontalSl_${key}`).append(htmObj[key]).show();
		$('.component30 .swiper-container').each(function(){
			let $1 = $(this);
			if($1.find('.swiper-slide').length < 5)
				$1.children().not('.swiper-wrapper').hide()
		});

		$('#otherleft div').each(function (index2, item2) {
			if (index2 === 0) {
				$(this).removeClass('mt20');
			}
		});

		$('#othermid div').each(function (index2, item2) {
			if (index2 === 0) {
				$(this).removeClass('mt20');
			}
		});
		$('#otherright div').each(function (index2, item2) {
			if (index2 === 0) {
				$(this).removeClass('mt20');
			}
		});
		setTimeout(function () {
			video();
		}, 500);
	}

	function otherMain(rotdid) {
		goOtherMain(rotdid);
	}

	function goDetailCourse(cotId) {
		location.href = `${mainurl}/curation/cr_abc_detail.do?cotId=${cotId}`
	}

	function getperiod(kind) {
		if (kind == 0)
			return '';
		else if (kind == 1)
			return '12';
		else
			return '23';
	}

	function getContentsType(contenttype) {
		if (contenttype == 12 || contenttype == 14 || contenttype == 28 || contenttype == 15) {
			return '<em class="type1"></em>';
		} else if (contenttype == 39) {
			return '<em class="type2"></em>';
		} else if (contenttype == 32) {
			return '<em class="type3"></em>';
		} else if (contenttype == 25) {
			return '<em class="type4"></em>';
		} else {
			return '<em class="type5"></em>';
		}
	}

	function getBroswer(useragent) {

		if (useragent.indexOf('Crosswalk') != -1)
			return 'Crosswalk';
		else if ((useragent.indexOf('chrome') != -1 || useragent.indexOf('crios') != -1) && useragent.indexOf('mobile') != -1)
			return 'Chrome Mobile WebView';
		else if (useragent.indexOf('msie') != -1)
			return 'IE';
		else if ((useragent.indexOf('chrome') == -1 && useragent.indexOf('crios') == -1)
			&& useragent.indexOf('mobile') != -1
			&& useragent.indexOf('safari') != -1)
			return 'Mobile Safari';
		else if (useragent.indexOf('samsungbrowser') != -1)
			return 'Samsung Internet';
		else if (useragent.indexOf('Whale') != -1)
			return 'Whale';

		return 'Chrome';
	}

	function getApp(useragent) {
		if (useragent.indexOf('naver') != -1 && useragent.indexOf('inapp') != -1)
			return 'naver';
		else if (useragent.indexOf('visitkor') != -1)
			return 'visitkor';
		else if (useragent.indexOf('kakaotalk') != -1 ||
			useragent.indexOf('facebook') != -1 ||
			useragent.indexOf('instagram') != -1)
			return 'etc';
		else
			return 'none';
	}

	function homeEnd() {
		let presentIdx = 0,
			activeItem = $(".accordion_box .pc li:first");
		const prev = $('.moVisu .swiper-button-prev'),
			next = $('.moVisu .swiper-button-next');

		if ($('#odsBanner li').length > 1) {
			let swiper2 = new Swiper('#odsBanner .swiper-container', {
				spaceBetween: 0,
				pagination: {
					el: '.swiper-pagination',
					clickable: true,
				},
				navigation: {
					nextEl: '.swiper-button-next',
					prevEl: '.swiper-button-prev',
				}, lazy: {
					loadPrevNext: true,
				}
			});
		} else
			$('#odsBanner .swiper-button-prev, #odsBanner .swiper-button-next').hide();

		video();

		$(".accordion_box .pc li").hover(function () {
			$(".accordion_box .pc li").removeClass("hover");
			$(this).addClass("hover");
			$(activeItem).animate({width: "80px"}, {duration: 300, queue: false});
			$(this).animate({width: "700px"}, {duration: 300, queue: false});
			activeItem = this;
		});
		$('.moVisu .swiper-container a').each(function (i) {
			if (!isSizeM)
				$(this).focus(() => {
					if (presentIdx < i) {
						next.trigger('click');
						presentIdx++;
					} else if (presentIdx > i) {
						prev.trigger('click');
						presentIdx--;
					}
				});
		});
		mkSwiper();
	}

	function goCurationContent(cotId, contenttitle, type, area) {
		
		$.ajax({
			url: mainurl + '/call',
			dataType: 'json',
			type: "POST",
			data: {
				cmd: 'CURATION_LOG_SAVE',
				device: isSizeM ? 'MOBILE' : 'PC',
				type: type,
				title: contenttitle,
				cotId: cotId,
				logtype: 'MAIN_CLICK',
				service: 'place'
			},
			success: goDetail(cotId)
		});
	}

	function CurationAiClickLogSave(cotId, contype, keywordtype) {
		let type = getContentsType2(Number(contype));
		$.ajax({
			url: mainurl + '/call',
			dataType: 'json',
			type: "POST",
			data: {
				cmd: 'CURATION_LOG_SAVE',
				device: isSizeM ? 'MOBILE' : 'PC',
				type: type,
				keywordtype: keywordtype,
				logtype: 'MAIN_CLICK',
				service: 'ai',
				page: 'SITE_MAIN'
			},
			success: goDetail(cotId)
		});
	}

	function getContentsType2(contenttype) {

		if (contenttype == 12 || contenttype == 14 || contenttype == 28 || contenttype == 15 || contenttype == 38) {
			return 'TRAVEL';
		} else if (contenttype == 39) {
			return 'RESTAURANT';
		} else if (contenttype == 32) {
			return 'ACCOMMODATION';
		} else if (contenttype == 25) {
			return 'COURSE';
		} else {
			return 'ARTICLE';
		}
	}

	function goCurationMain() {
		let sigungucodes = '0';
		$("input:checkbox[name=areaChk]:checked").each(function () {
			let sigungucode = $(this).parent().attr('id');
			sigungucodes += ',' + sigungucode;
		});
		let areacode = $("input:radio[name=areaChk]:checked").attr('id');
		areacode = areacode.replace('area_chk', '')
		saveAreaClickLog(areacode, sigungucodes.split(","))
		location.href = "/main/cr_main.do?areacode=" + areacode + "&sigungucode=" + sigungucodes;
	}

	function sigunguOpen() {
		if ($('#curationAreaPop .s_menu .btn_smenu').hasClass('on')) {
			$('#curationAreaPop .s_menu ul').css('display', 'none');
			$('.s_menu .btn_smenu').removeClass('on');
			layerPopup.layerUpdate('curationAreaPop');
		} else {
			$('#curationAreaPop .s_menu .btn_smenu').addClass('on');
			$('#curationAreaPop .s_menu ul').css('display', '');
			layerPopup.layerUpdate('curationAreaPop');
		}

	}

	function replaceAll(str, searchStr, replaceStr) {
		return str.split(searchStr).join(replaceStr);
	}

	function setCurationRandomTab() {
		const number = Math.round(Math.random());
		switch (number) {
			case 0: {
				$('.menu2').addClass('on')
				$('.menu3').removeClass('on')
				getCurationAiContents()
			}
				break
			case 1:
			default: {
				$('.menu2').removeClass('on')
				$('.menu3').addClass('on')
                getCurationPlannerBestContents()
			}
				break
		}
	}

	function ios_go_url(Id) {
		let url = "youtube://watch?v=" + Id;
		location.href = url;

		if (getBrowser().indexOf('Opera') != -1) {
			url = "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=" + Id;
			location.href = url;
			setTimeout(function () {
				window.location.href = "http://itunes.apple.com/kr/app/id544007664?mt=8";
			}, 1000);

		} else {
			setTimeout(function () {
				window.location.href = "http://itunes.apple.com/kr/app/id544007664?mt=8";
			}, 1000);
		}
	}

	function closebutton(kind) {
		if (kind == 1) {
			setCookie('forecast_1', 'Y', 1);
			$('.mbti_quick').remove();
		} else {
			setCookie('forecast_2', 'Y', 1);
			$('.mbti_quick').remove();
		}
	}

	function mbtiBtnScroll() {
		$('.event_quick a').click(function () {
			$('html, body').animate({
				scrollTop: $($.attr(this, 'href')).offset().top
			}, 500);
			return false;
		});
		let btnW = $('.event_quick')
			, btnTop = btnW.find('.close');

		let $w = $(window),
			footerHei = $('#footer').outerHeight(),
			$banner = $('.event_quick');

		$w.on('scroll', function () {

			let sT = $w.scrollTop(),
				val = $(document).height() - $w.height() - footerHei;

			if (sT >= val)
				$banner.addClass('on')
			else
				$banner.removeClass('on')

		});

		btnTop.click(function () {
			btnW.addClass('none');
		});
	}

	function WindowopenCheck(linkurl, linkfileurl, cotId) {

		if (cotId != 'undefined' && cotId != '' && cotId != undefined)
			return '';

		if (cotId != 'undefined' && cotId != '' && cotId != undefined)
			return '';
		else if (linkurl != 'undefined' && linkurl != '' && linkurl != undefined) {
			if (linkurl.indexOf(mainurl) > -1) {
				return '';
			} else {
				return 'title=""';
			}
		} else if (linkfileurl != 'undefined' && linkfileurl != '') {
			if (appYn == 'Y') {
				return 'title=""';
			} else {
				return 'title=""';
			}
		} else {
			return '';
		}

	}

	function mainPopupSlide() {
		let swiper = new Swiper('#safetyStay1 .swiper-container', {
			loop: true,
			pagination: {
				el: '.slide_pop .swiper-pagination',
				type: 'bullets',
				observer: true,
				observeParents: true,
				clickable: true,
				renderBullet: function (index, className) {
					return '<button type="button" class="' + className + '"><span class="blind">' + (index + 1) + '  </span></button>';
				}
			},

			autoplay: {
				delay: 3000,
			},
			on: {
				init: function () {
					swiperTabindex('.slide_pop', this.activeIndex);
				},
				slideChangeTransitionEnd: function () {
					swiperTabindex('.slide_pop', this.activeIndex);
				}
			}
		});

		$('.slide_pop .swiper-wrapper').on('focusin', function () {
			$(this).closest('.slide_pop').addClass('active');
			swiper.autoplay.stop();
		})

		$('.slide_pop .btn_autoArea button').on('click', function () {
			if ($(this).closest('.slide_pop').hasClass('active')) {
				$(this).closest('.slide_pop').removeClass('active');
				swiper.autoplay.start();
			} else {
				$(this).closest('.slide_pop').addClass('active');
				swiper.autoplay.stop();
			}
		});

		$('.slide_pop .swiper-pagination button').on('click', function () {
			if ($('.slide_pop').addClass('active')) {
				swiper.autoplay.stop();
			}
		});

	}

	function mkSwiper() {

				draggable: true

				el: '.swiper-pagination',
				clickable: true,
			},
			navigation: {
				nextEl: '.swiper-button-next',
				prevEl: '.swiper-button-prev',
			},
		});
	}

	function switchPCNM() {

		} else {
			MainChoice = 'MainMo';
			otdId = 'ab097fc9-daa6-423d-8fcb-50aec7852e21';

		}
	}

	function scSwiper() {
		const el = $(isSizeM ? '#mainContainerM' : '#mainContainerPC').find('.main_showcase'),
				setBg = ($this) => el.css('background', $($this).data('color')),
				spb = el.find('.swiper-progress-bar'),
				galleryThumbs = new Swiper(el.find('.gallery-thumbs'), {
					spaceBetween: 0,
					slidesPerView: "auto",
					speed: 1000,
					loop: true,
					pagination: {
						el: el.find('.swiper-pagination'),
						type: 'fraction',
						formatFractionCurrent: (number) => ('0' + number).slice(-2),
						formatFractionTotal: (number) => ('0' + number).slice(-2)
					},
					navigation: {
						nextEl: '.swiper-button-next',
						prevEl: '.swiper-button-prev'
					},
					on: {
						init: function () {
							spb.removeClass("animate");
							spb.removeClass("active");
							spb.eq(0).addClass("animate");
							spb.eq(0).addClass("active");
							swiperTabindex(el.selector, this.activeIndex);
							isPossibleChangeBg.call(this);
						},
						slideChangeTransitionStart: function(){
							spb.removeClass("animate");
							spb.removeClass("active");
							spb.eq(0).addClass("active");
						},
						slideChangeTransitionEnd: function(){
							spb.eq(0).addClass("animate");
							swiperTabindex(el.selector, this.activeIndex);
						},
						activeIndexChange: function(){
							isPossibleChangeBg.call(this);
						}
					}
				}),
				galleryTop = new Swiper(el.find('.gallery-top'), { //
					spaceBetween: 30,
					slidesPerView: "auto",
					loop: true,
					speed: 1000,
					on: {
						init: function(){
							isPossibleChangeBg.call(this, true);
						},
						activeIndexChange: function(){
							isPossibleChangeBg.call(this, true);
						}
					}
				});

		galleryTop.controller.control = galleryThumbs;
		galleryThumbs.controller.control = galleryTop;

		el.on('focusin', '.swiper-wrapper', function () {
			el.addClass('active');
			galleryThumbs.autoplay.stop();
			galleryTop.autoplay.stop();
		}).on('click', '.btn_auto button', function () {
            if (!el.hasClass('active')) {
                el.addClass('active');
                $(this).text('');
            } else {
                el.removeClass('active');
                $(this).text('');
            }
		}).on('click', '.swiper-pagination button', () => {
			if (el.addClass('active')) {
				$scSwiper.autoplay.stop();
				galleryTop.autoplay.stop();
			}
		}).on('click', '.swiper-button-prev, .swiper-button-next', () => {
			el.addClass('active');
		});
		setInterval(() => {
			if(spb.find('.fill')[0].offsetWidth / spb.children().width() === 1)
				galleryTop.slideNext();
		}, 500)
		function isPossibleChangeBg(mb){
			!(mb ^ isSizeM) && setBg(this.slides[this.realIndex]);
		}
		$(document).on('click', '.main_showcase .btn_auto button', function(){
			if($(this).closest('.main_showcase').hasClass('active'))
				$('.main_showcase .btn_autoPlay').focus();
			else
				$('.main_showcase .btn_autoStop').focus();
		});
	}

	const pavilion = {
		id: 'b1f1d84c-e1cf-11ed-b570-0242ac1b0002',
		getSpecialPavilion: function(type){
			return $.ajax({
				type: 'POST',
				url: mainurl + '/call',
				data: {cmd: 'MAIN_SPECIAL_PAVILION', type},
				error: console.log
			});
		},
		setSpecialPavilion: function({body: {result}}){
			const el = $container.find('.special_box'),
					cont = el.children('.cont'),
					img = cont.children('.img'),
					master = result.master;

			if(!master.viewStatus || result.contentByMenu.length === 0) return;
			const groupedContentByMenu = result.contentByMenu.reduce((result, content) => {
				const { compOrder, ...rest } = content;

				if (!result[compOrder])
					result[compOrder] = [];
				result[compOrder].push(rest);
				return result;
			}, []);
			let menu = '';

			el.children('.bg').css('background', master.bgColor + (master.bgTypeStatus ? ' url(' + mainimgurl + (!smallerThanTablet() && $(window).width() <= 1535 ? master.tabletbgDescImg : master.bgDescImg) + ')no-repeat 50%' : ''));
			cont.find('.tag').html(master.secTit);
			cont.find('.mtit').html(`<a href="javascript:mainLogAndMove('${pavilion.id}','${master.linkUrl}');">${master.mTit}</a>`);
			cont.find('.stit').html(master.sTit);
			if(master.dateStatus == 1) {
				cont.find('.day').html(`${conDateFormat(removeSpecialChars(master.startDate), `yyyy. M. d.`)} ~ ${conDateFormat(removeSpecialChars(master.endDate), `yyyy. M. d.`)}`);
			}
			img.html(`<img src="${mainimgurl + master.bgImg}" alt="">`);

			groupedContentByMenu.forEach((e, i) => {
				let conList = `<li class="swiper-container" style="visibility:hidden;left:-9999px">
					<div class="swiper-wrapper">`;

				e.forEach((e2, i2) => e.length !== 1 && i2 === 0 ?
						menu += `<div class="swiper-slide ${i === 0 ? ` on` : ``}"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="pavilion.changeTab(this);">${e2.title}</a></div>` :
						conList += `<div class="swiper-slide"><a href="javascript:mainLogAndMove(\'${pavilion.id}\', \'${e2.linkUrl || '/detail/detail_view.do?cotid=' + e2.cotId}\')">
						<img src="` + mainimgurl + e2.imgId + `" alt="` + e2.imgDescrition + `"></a></div>`);
				conList += `</div>
						<div class="page">
							<div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
							<div class="btn_auto">
								<button class="btn_autoStop"></button>
							<div>
						</div>
					</div>`;
				el.find('.list .banner').append(conList);
				el.find('.menu .swiper-wrapper').html(menu);
			});

			let menuCnt = $container.find('.special_box .menu .swiper-wrapper').find('.swiper-slide').length;
			if (menuCnt == 1) {
				$('.special_box .menu .swiper-slide a').addClass('default');
				$('.main_mo .special_box .menu .swiper-slide.on a').removeAttr('href').removeAttr('onclick')
			}
			el.show();
			pavilion.slider();
			setTimeout(() => el.find('.list .banner .swiper-container').css('visibility', 'visible').siblings().slice(1).css('position', 'absolute'), 1000);
			if (window.innerWidth >= 767 && window.innerWidth <= 1024)
				img.addClass('type1');
		},
		slider: () => {
			let menu = new Swiper($container.find(".special_box .menu .swiper-container"), {
				spaceBetween: smallerThanTablet() ? 5 : 10,
				watchOverflow: true,
				slidesPerView: "auto",
				navigation: {
					nextEl: ".special_box .menu .swiper-button-next",
					prevEl: ".special_box .menu .swiper-button-prev",
				},
				on: {
					init: function () {
						updateMenu(this);
					}
				},
			});

			function updateMenu(swiper) {
				if (!swiper.isEnd || !swiper.isBeginning) {
					$container.find(".special_box .menu").addClass("type1");
				} else {
					$container.find(".special_box .menu").removeClass("type1");
				}
			}

			function pcSpcBanner() {
				var specialPcBanner = new Swiper($container.find(".special_box .banner .swiper-container"), {
					spaceBetween: 20,
					centeredSlides: false,
					slidesPerView: "auto",
					loop: $(".special_box .banner .swiper-slide").length != 3,
					autoplay: {
						delay: 3000,
						pauseOnMouseEnter: true,
						disableOnInteraction: false,
					},
					pagination: {
						el: ".special_box .banner .swiper-pagination",
						type: "fraction",
						formatFractionCurrent: function (number) {
							return ('0' + number).slice(-2);
						},
						formatFractionTotal: function (number) {
							return ('0' + number).slice(-2);
						},
					},
					on : {
						init : function () {
							if($(".special_box .banner .swiper-slide").length < 4){
								$('.special_box .banner .swiper-container').addClass('lock');
								this.params.watchOverflow = true;
								this.update();
							}
						},
					},
				});

				$('.special_box .banner .swiper-wrapper').on('focusin', function(){
					$(this).closest('.special_box .banner').addClass('active');
					specialPcBanner.autoplay.stop();
					$('.special_box .banner .btn_auto button').text('');
				});
				$('.special_box .banner .btn_auto button').on('click', function(){
					if($(this).closest('.special_box .banner').hasClass('active')){
						$(this).closest('.special_box .banner').removeClass('active');
						specialPcBanner.autoplay.start();
						$(this).text('');
					}else{
						$(this).closest('.special_box .banner').addClass('active');
						specialPcBanner.autoplay.stop();
						$(this).text('');
					}
				});
			}

			function moSpcBanner(){
				if($('.special_box .banner .swiper-container .swiper-slide').length > 2){
					$('.special_box .banner').addClass('js_slider');
					var specialMoBanner = new Swiper('.special_box .banner .swiper-container', {
						spaceBetween: 0,
						loop:true,
						centeredSlides : true,
						slidesPerView: "auto",
						autoplay: {
							delay: 3000,
							pauseOnMouseEnter: true,
							disableOnInteraction: false,
						},
						pagination: {
							el: ".special_box .banner .swiper-pagination",
							type: "fraction",
							formatFractionCurrent: function (number) {
								return ('0' + number).slice(-2);
							},
							formatFractionTotal: function (number) {
								return ('0' + number).slice(-2);
							},
						},
					});
					$('.special_box .banner .swiper-wrapper').on('focusin', function(){
						$(this).closest('.special_box .banner').addClass('active');
						specialMoBanner.autoplay.stop();
						$('.special_box .banner .btn_auto button').text('');
					});
					$('.special_box .banner .btn_auto button').on('click', function(){
						if($(this).closest('.special_box .banner').hasClass('active')){
							$(this).closest('.special_box .banner').removeClass('active');
							specialMoBanner.autoplay.start();
							$(this).text('');
						}else{
							$(this).closest('.special_box .banner').addClass('active');
							specialMoBanner.autoplay.stop();
							$(this).text('');
						}
					});
				}
			}

			if (smallerThanTablet())
				moSpcBanner();
			else
				pcSpcBanner();

			// $('.main_mo .special_box .menu').addClass('type1');
		},
		changeTab: function(_this) {
			const p = $(_this).parent(),
					idx = p.index();

			goMainLogSave(this.id);
			p.addClass('on').siblings().removeClass('on');
			$container.find('.special_box .list .banner .swiper-container').eq(idx).css('position','static').siblings().css('position','absolute');
		}
	}

	//  
	function getCurationPlaceContents(aicheck, code, afterLoad) {
		const limit = 4,
				wrap = $('.main_curation_area');

		if(window.location.hash) {
			//hash   ^    string    .
			var str_hash = window.location.hash;
			str_hash = str_hash.replace("#","");
			arr_param=str_hash.split("^");
			hashcode = arr_param[0];

			if(hashcode != "home") {
				code = hashcode;
			}
		}

		wrap.addClass('dim');
		loadQuration({
			device: isSizeM ? 'MOBILE' : 'PC',
			limit,
			curationType: 'MAIN_A',
			...(code && {areaCode: code})
		}).done(({data: data}) => {
			setCurationPlaceContents(data, aicheck, code, afterLoad);
			try {
				___traceCurationSiteMain(data.items, 'HOT')
			} catch (e) {
				if (!isProduction)
					console.error(e)
			}
			$('.main_curation_area').removeClass('dim');
		}).fail(() => wrap.css('display', 'none').removeClass('dim'));
	}

	function setCurationPlaceContents(data, aicheck, code, afterLoad) {
		let htm = ``,
				imgUri = ``;

		$.each(data, function (idx, item) {
			let viewcontenttitle = item.viewContent;
			const like = $.cookie('content_' + item.cotId) === 'Y';

			if (!viewcontenttitle)
				viewcontenttitle = item.content.displayTitle;

			imgUri = mainimgurl + item.imgId + '&mode=progress';
			// imgUri = mainimgurl + item.imgId;
			// imgUri = 'https://cdn.visitkorea.or.kr/img/call?cmd=VIEW&id=' + item.imgId + '&mode=progress';
			htm += `<li onclick="___traceCurationConsume(this)" data-curation-type="HOT" data-page="SITE_MAIN" data-content-order="` + (idx + 1) + `" data-cot-id="` + item.cotId + `" data-content-type="` + item.content.contentType + `"${isSizeM ? ' class="swiper-slide"' : ''}>
							<a href="javascript:goCurationContent('` + item.cotId + `', '` + viewcontenttitle + `', '` + item.typeCode + `', '` + code + `');">
							<div class="img_scale" style="height:100%">
								<div class="img_wrap" style="background-image:url(` + imgUri + `)"></div>
							</div>
							<strong>` + viewcontenttitle + `</strong>
						</a>
						<button type="button" class="good${like ? ' on' : ''}" title="${like ? '' : ''}" onclick="setLike2('${item.cotId}', this);"></button>
					</li>`;
		});

		if (aicheck) {
			$container.find('.exhaust ul').html(htm);
			$container.find('.exhaust').show();
		} else
			eval(`$container.find('.main_curation_area .hot').` + (isSizeM ? `find('.swiper-wrapper').` : ``) + `html(htm)`);

		isSizeM && new Swiper($container.find(".main_curation_area .tab_cont .hot .swiper-container"), {
			spaceBetween: 10,
			watchOverflow: true,
			slidesPerView: "auto",
			observer: true,
			centeredSlides: true,
			observeParents: true,
			loop: true,
			pagination: {
				el: ".swiper-pagination",
				type: "progressbar",
			},
		});

		!afterLoad && setArea(code);
	}

	// AI 
	function getCurationAiContents() {
		const data = {},
				useragent = navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase();

		data.appType = getApp(useragent);
		data.browser = getBroswer(useragent);
		data.offset = CURATION_AI_CNT;
		data.os = getDevice();
		data.sourcePageType = 'SITE_MAIN';
		data.cache = false;

		let url = new URL(mainurl + '/api/v2/curation/ai');
		Object.entries(data).forEach(data => url.searchParams.append(data[0], data[1]));

		$('.main_curation_area').addClass('dim');
		$('.main_curation_area .loading').css('display', '');
		fetch(url, {
			headers: {
				"Content-Type": "application/json",
				"X-SNS-ID": snsId,
			}
		}).then(response => response.json()).then(data => {
			if (data.code === 0) {
				setCurationAiContents(data.data);
				try {
					___traceCurationSiteMain(data.data.items, 'AI')
				} catch (e) {
					if (!isProduction) {
						console.error(e)
					}
				}
			} else AiContentsDisable();
			$('.main_curation_area').removeClass('dim');
		}).catch((error) => {
			console.log(error)
			$('.main_curation_area').removeClass('dim');
			// $('.main_curation_area').css('display','none');
		});
	}

	function setCurationAiContents(data) {
		const isLike = (cotId) => $.cookie(`content_${cotId}`) === 'Y';
		let htm = '';

		if (!data || !data.items || data.items.length === 0 || data.items.length < CURATION_AI_CNT) {
			AiContentsDisable();
			return;
		}
		$('.ai_out, .aigodiv').hide();
		$container.find('.ai_list').show();
		$.each(data.items, function (index, item) {
			const imgUri = mainimgurl + (item.detailArticle ? item.detailArticle.imgId : item.detailDatabase.firstImage) + '&mode=progress';
			// const imgUri = mainimgurl + (item.detailArticle ? item.detailArticle.imgId : item.detailDatabase.firstImage);
			const addr = item.detailDatabase.addr1.split(" ").slice(0, 2).join(" ");
			const like = isLike(item.cotId);

			htm += `<li onclick="___traceCurationConsume(this)" data-curation-type="AI" data-page="SITE_MAIN" data-content-order="${index + 1}" data-cot-id="${item.cotId}" data-content-type="${item.contentType}">
					<div>
						<a href="javascript:CurationAiClickLogSave('${item.cotId}', '${item.contentType}', '${data.actionInfo.keywordType}');">
								<div class="img_wrap" style="background-image:url(` + imgUri + `)"></div>
							<strong${isSizeM ? ' style="display:none"' : ''}>${item.title}</strong>
							<span${isSizeM ? ' style="display:none"' : ''}>${addr}</span>
						</a>
						<button type="button" class="good${like ? ' on' : ''}" title="${like ? '' : ''}" ${isSizeM ? ' style="display:none"' : ''} onclick="setLike2('${item.cotId}', this);"></button>
					</div>
				</li>`;
		});
		$container.find('.ai_list ul').html(htm);
		if(isSizeM){
			const _clone = (el, like) => {
				const $el = el.clone();

				$el.find('strong, span, button').show();
				like && $el.find('.good').addClass('on');
				$container.find('.ai_list .bimg').html($el);
			}

			_clone($container.find('.ai_list ul li:eq(0)'));
			$container.find('.ai_list li > div').on('click', function(e){
				e.preventDefault();
				_clone($(this), isLike($(this).parent().data('cot-id')));
			})
		}
	}

	function getCurationPlannerBestContents() {
		const data = {};
		data.device = isSizeM ? 'MOBILE' : 'PC';
		data.sourcePageType = 'SITE_MAIN';
		data.offset = 3;

		let url = new URL(mainurl + '/api/v2/abc-market/best-course');
		// let url = new URL('https://dev.ktovisitkorea.com/api/v2/abc-market/best-course');
		Object.entries(data).forEach(data => url.searchParams.append(data[0], data[1]));
		$('.main_curation_area').addClass('dim');
		$('.main_curation_area .loading').css('display', '');
		fetch(url, {
			headers: {
				"Content-Type": "application/json",
				"X-SNS-ID": snsId,
				"cache-control": "no-cache"
			}
		}).then(response => response.json()).then(data => {
			setCurationAbcContents(data.code === 0 ? data.data : null);
			$('.main_curation_area').removeClass('dim');
			new Swiper("#mainContainerM .main_curation_area .abc .swiper-container", {
				slideToClickedSlide: true,
				centeredSlides: true,
				slidesPerView: 'auto',
				observer: true,
				observeParents: true,
			});
		}).catch((error) =>{
			console.log(error);
		});
	}

	function AiContentsDisable() {
		$container.find('.ai_out, .aigodiv').show();
		$container.find('.ai_condiv, .ai_list').hide();
		if (loginYn !== 'Y')
			$('.ai_out').html('<strong> AI    .</strong>'
					+ '<p>       .</p>'
					+ '<a href="javascript:showLogin(1);" class="login"> </a>'
			)
		else {
			$('.ai_out').hide();
			getCurationPlaceContents(true);
		}
	}

	function setCurationAbcContents(data) {
		let settingMainPlannerTitleHtml = ``
		if (snsUsrName === undefined) {
			if (!isSizeM) {
				settingMainPlannerTitleHtml += `1 !     .`
			} else {
				settingMainPlannerTitleHtml += `1 ! <br>    .`
			}
		} else {
			if (!isSizeM) {
				settingMainPlannerTitleHtml += `1 ! <strong>` + snsUsrName + `</strong>,     .`
			} else {
				settingMainPlannerTitleHtml += `1 ! <strong>` + snsUsrName + `</strong>, <br>    .`
			}
		}
		if (isSizeM) {
			$('.main_curation_area .mainplannerBtnMo').html(settingMainPlannerTitleHtml)
		} else {
			$('.main_curation_area .mainplannerBtnPc').html(settingMainPlannerTitleHtml)
		}

		let htm = '';
		let region = '';
    let profileImg = ''

		data.items.forEach((items, index) => {
			if(items.sns.profileChk ==='Y') {
				profileImg = mainimgurl + items.sns.profileId
			} else {
				profileImg = items.imagePath
				if(profileImg != null && profileImg != '') {
					profileImg = profileImg.replace('http://', 'https://');
					profileImg = profileImg.replace('th-p.talk.kakao.co.kr', 'k.kakaocdn.net');
				}
			}
			let createDate = replaceAll(items.modifiedAt.substring(0, 10), '-', '');
			if(items.codes.length > 1) {
				region = getAreaName(items.codes[0].sido) + ' ' + getSigunguName(items.codes[0].sido, items.codes[0].sgg)
						+ ' ~ ' + getAreaName(items.codes[1].sido) + ' ' + getSigunguName(items.codes[1].sido, items.codes[1].sgg)
			} else {
				region = getAreaName(items.codes[0].sido) + ' ' + getSigunguName(items.codes[0].sido, items.codes[0].sgg)
			}
			htm += `<li${isSizeM ? ' class="swiper-slide"' : ''}>
				<a href="javascript:goDetailCourse('${items.cotId}');">
					<span class="best">BEST</span>
					<div class="img_scale">
						<div class="img_wrap"
							style="background-image:url(` + mainimgurl + items.thumbnail + `);"></div>
					</div>
					<div class="info">`;
			if( (snsId === undefined) || (items.sns.id !== snsId) ) {
				htm += ` <span class="profile"><img src=${profileImg} onerror="this.remove();" alt=""></span>`;
			}
			htm+=`<em>${getperiod(items.period)}</em>
						<strong>${items.title}</strong>
						<span class="area">${region}</span>
						<span></span>
						<span>${conDateFormat(createDate,'yyyyMMdd','.')}</span>
					</div>
				</a>
			</li>`;
		});
		$('#tabMenu02 .more_view > button').show();
		eval(`$container.find('.abcList').` + (isSizeM ? `find('.swiper-wrapper').` : ``) + `html(htm).show()`);
	}

	function mSlide() {
		new Swiper("#mainContainerM .main_curation_area .area_tab .swiper-container", {
			spaceBetween: 5,
			watchOverflow: true,
			slidesPerView: "auto",
			observer: true,
			observeParents: true,
		});
		new Swiper(".component29 .swiper-container", {
			spaceBetween: 15,
			watchOverflow: true,
			slidesPerView: "auto",
			observer: true,
			centeredSlides: true,
			observeParents: true,
			loop: true,
			pagination: {
				el: ".swiper-pagination",
				type: "progressbar",
			},
		});
	}

	function setArea(code){
		const arr = ['', '', '', '', '', '', '', '','', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''];
		let areaIdx = arr.indexOf(getAreaName(code)),
				htm = ``;

		if(areaIdx === -1)
			areaIdx = 0;

		if(isSizeM) {
			htm += `<div class="swiper-container">
						<ul class="swiper-wrapper">`;
			arr.forEach((item, idx) => htm += `<li class="swiper-slide"><button type="button" class="${idx === 0 ? 'all' : ''}${idx === areaIdx ? ' on' : ''}">${item}</button></li>`);
			htm += `	</ul>
					</div>`;
		}else {
			htm += `<ul class="swiper-wrapper">`;
			arr.forEach((item, idx) => htm += `<li><button type="button" class="${idx === 0 ? 'all' : ''}${idx === areaIdx ? ' on' : ''}">${item}</button></li>`);
			htm += `</ul>`;
		}
		$container.find('.main_curation_area .area_tab').html(htm);
		isSizeM && new Swiper($container.find(".main_curation_area .area_tab .swiper-container"), {
			spaceBetween: 5,
			watchOverflow: true,
			slidesPerView: "auto",
			observer: true,
			observeParents: true,
		});
		$('.area_tab ul li button.all').attr('title','');
	}

	if ($('.quick_menu.app')) {
		setTimeout(function () {
			$('.box_footer').addClass('padding');
		}, 500);
	}
